  <summary date="2015-01-26T17:45:12Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Stop Motorcycle Checkpoint Funding Act 

 Prohibits the Secretary of Transportation (DOT) from providing a grant or any funds to a state, county, town, township, Indian tribe, municipality, or other local government for any program to: (1) check motorcycle helmet use, or (2) create motorcycle checkpoints that specifically target motorcycle operators or motorcycle passengers.</summary>
